Package com.incoming.pvnsdk

Implementations of the API interfaces described in com.incoming.pvnsdk.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataAccessService
    Placeholder for data access API.
    NotificationActionType  
    VideoDescriptor
    Describes a video and provides the video file location.
    VideoPlaybackEventService
    Used to record events generated by a video player.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IncomingApiServiceLocator
    Provides access to the Incoming SDK API.
    PushVideo
    The main class used to configure the Push Video SDK.
    PushVideoAdManager
    Host applications that wish to deliver advertisements should use the advertising SDK of their choice to implement this adapter and register for to receives requests to play advertisements at PushVideo.configureAdManager(PushVideoAdManager).
